OASISFormat: 0.4
Name: macaque
Version: 0.7.2
Synopsis: MaCaQue (or macaque) is a DSL for SQL Queries in Caml
Description: Macaque produces SQL requests from a comprehension syntax.
  It can build queries by from simpler components, using phantom types
  used to ensure safety.
Maintainers: Jacques-Pascal Deplaix <jp.deplaix@gmail.com>
Authors:
  Gabriel Scherer <gasche.dylc@gmail.com>,
  Jérôme Vouillon <jp.deplaix@gmail.com>
License: LGPL-2 with OCaml linking exception
Homepage: https://github.com/ocsigen/macaque
Plugins: DevFiles (0.4), META (0.4)
AlphaFeatures: compiled_setup_ml
BuildTools: ocamlbuild

